name: Twin Flames
description:
One of the main characteristics of a twin flame relationship is that it will be both challenging & healing due to the mirrored nature of a twin flame.

This OBJKT represents our relationship in many ways.

We created this piece leading up to Halloween a time where a lot of artist are burning off excess art and seasonal pieces.

We are toasting marshmallows in the flames of the great burn and coming together closer as a couple and as artists.

This image was created from photographs or drawing from @allykhat328 & @artdirtybastard
